{
  "chapter": 44,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十四回\"神秘五行宫\"中，宝玉与小公主暗中观察王大娘以鸳鸯双剑击败万老夫人。万老夫人被擒后，李名生现身，原来他已投靠王大娘，与一群少女关系暧昧。宝玉决定追赶救人，追踪众人穿越密道进入一处隐秘盆地——五行宫。王大娘以礼相待，小公主竟与王大娘相识，令宝玉大为惊讶。经王大娘解释，桑林惨变另有隐情，李名生所述并非全假。万老夫人透露她是暗中跟踪铁髯、如意等人至此，发现他们在泰山之会后暗中调度弟子，行踪诡秘。本章揭示了王大娘的神秘势力、万老夫人被擒的真相，以及铁髯等人暗中活动的重要线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "问问你也不好么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你莫非是在讨我的好？你……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你在我面前，有时处处要占强，处处要压倒我，有时又装葱装蒜装呆子，好像什么都不懂……你为何要如此？当我是小孩么？",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "可惜你已不再是以前那只喜欢插花的孩子了……假如你还是孩子，那有多好……那有多好……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是她。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "七年不见，不想她竟在这里出现。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "谁说七年不见，泰山上我还见着她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你说的是万老夫人，我说的却是另一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "另一个？另一个是谁？你也认得？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "此人的来历说来话长，我只能告诉你她叫王大娘，就是那王半侠的妻子，别的事慢慢再说吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "王半侠？……王大娘……她怎会又和万老夫人动起手来……万老夫人为何还未回到白水宫？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "万老夫人？白水宫？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "万老夫人八成已被……已被你那丈母娘收买了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "这就对了，万老夫人既已是白水宫属下，且不愿我到白水宫去，和那李名生相约在此地的人，想必就是她。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错……哼！你怎的突然又变聪明了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我本来就不笨。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你这……",
      "tone": "娇嗔",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "臭婆娘，臭残废，我又没宰你爹爹，也没抢你的老公，你和我有什么深仇大恨，倒真像要和我老婆子拼命似的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "谁和你拼命，我只是要你的命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "你可知道我老婆子是谁么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我若不知道你是谁，也不要你的命了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "你认得我，你与我有何仇恨？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你猜猜看？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "猜不着……猜不着。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "王大娘到底和万老夫人有何仇恨，你可知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "只怕为的是万大侠。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "瞧这王大娘武功，已有数次可将万老夫人置之死地，但她却迟迟不出手，这……这又是为的什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "意在活擒，不在取命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "对了，她活擒了万老夫人，便可将万子良诱来，但是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "若论贪生怕死，只怕没人比得上她。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "臭残废！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "可是要将那肉球宰了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "不忙，先带回去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "你……你这孙子原来和这臭婆娘是一党。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你莫管我是一党两党，反正你要我做的事，我倒真替你做了，你还有什么可埋怨的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "你可瞧见了方宝玉么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "自然瞧见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "他长得是不是真的很俊？武功是不是真的很高？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "你问什么？你再问人家也不会看上你。告诉你，小白脸都没有好东西，还是年纪大些的好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "还是你好，是么？羞不羞，你这老风骚。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "方宝玉，想不到你不但武功出名，连人长得俊也出名了。人家这么样打听你，想必是中意你了，你高兴么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "嗯什么？说话呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "走！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "走？哪里去？去追她们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "不错，追她们，救回万老夫人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "救她？为什么要救她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "一来为万大侠，二来为查明真象。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "为何不赶上去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "先瞧瞧他们要去哪里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "既已来了，还等什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你既要救回万老夫人，既要查明真象，迟早都是要和人家对面的，倒不如此刻就索性光明堂皇地走进去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "这话也有理。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "鹦鹉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "客来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "鹦鹉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "客来了……客来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "不想一只鸟几乎吓到了方大侠。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘请了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你是谁？来干什么的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "你这是来相亲的，还是来找麻烦的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "找麻烦，找什么麻烦？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "他就是方宝玉，来找你们要人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方宝玉。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "还发什么呆，往里面闯呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "贵客光临，恕贱妾身带残疾，不能远迎，快请进来，容贱妾待茶。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "宝玉遵命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "王大娘可还认得方宝玉？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "我怎会不认得你？除了方宝玉外，世上哪里还有第二个这么英俊、这么可爱的少年人？",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "王大娘，你好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "哎哟！小公主，没多久不见，你可越来越标致了，今儿若不是方少侠来，只怕我可再也请不到你。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "你再说……谁知道你住在这里呀！",
      "tone": "娇嗔",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你不知道么？我才不信。火宫主没有告诉你么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "谁也没有告诉我，就好像你这地方比什么都神秘似的，我真不懂，这儿到底有什么神秘呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你……你原来认得她。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "我几时说过不认得她？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "不错，你是没说过。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "喂！万老夫人已出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你知道了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那桑林中的小屋，想必也是王大娘的属下在住着，所以火魔神才会将我约来这里……是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错，不但那屋子是我的，那桑林也是我的……你知道，女孩子们闲着没事做，就想养些蚕宝宝。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "所以李名生所说的老陈也全都是假的，他根本什么也没瞧见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "这不是我有意骗你，而是王……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "桑林发生的惨变，我本也不知道。想来那些人手脚必很快，等你们来了，我才瞧见。我知道你们必定不知该去哪里，所以才让李名生去通知你们，只因火宫主门下来借房子的时候，我已瞧见下一站是大名府了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "但我们所说的那些话，倒并非全是假的，只因我虽没有瞧见他们动手，铁金刀却瞧见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "莫非是他告诉你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "他在暗中偷偷瞧了个明白，便赶紧退下，却不想恰巧遇到了我，于是，他便自我口中知道你一定会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "你当真是他朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "不但是朋友，而且昔日还曾同门学艺，而且还是他师兄，只是……唉！我对练武总是打不起精神，所以……所以……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "世事当真奇妙得很，不想这点我也猜错了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李名生",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "世上巧事原本不少，等你到我这年纪，你就会知道了，否则又怎会让我一出来就遇到万老夫人。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "万老夫人自然是认得你的，她不愿我去白水宫，是以便令你前来骗我，却不知你已是王大娘的……的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "而这所有的事，你原已全都知道了，但你却偏偏装模作样，百般捉弄我，让我变成个大大的呆子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错，我什么都早巳知道了，我完全是在故意捉弄你，当你是呆子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你既已骗我，又何必……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "她没有骗你，你冤枉她了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "我怎会冤枉她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "这一切事，她本不知道，她也真的不知道我住在这里，更不知道李名生已跟着我，自也不知道李名生的话是真是假。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "我……我难道错了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你错了，你完全错了，你不但冤枉了她，也冤枉了我老人家。你这小呆子，自以为什么都懂，什么都知道，却不知世上有些事是你永远也猜不到的，你不过总是在自作聪明而已。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我冤枉了你什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "你可知道我老人家怎会来到这里？凑巧么？世上哪有这么多凑巧的事？我是一路跟着人来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "谁？跟着谁来的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "那些人你也认得，我一路自泰山跟着他们来到这里，这一路上他们所做的事，没有一件能逃得过我的眼睛。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "这些人究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "我老了，又老又贪吃，没有些好东西吃，我连话也说不动了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "这容易，这里的东西，随便你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "我口也渴了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "能让方少侠侍候你，你福气倒不小。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "他能听到我老人家说的话，福气更不小。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你老人家现在可以说了么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "我是跟着铁髯、如意这几个老儿来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是他们。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "泰山之会散后，我老人家也混进了万竹山庄，但那时你竟已走了，我老人家本觉有些失望，哪知……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "怎样……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_bao_yu",
      "text": "我竟发觉铁髯、如意那几个老不死竟在暗中调度弟子，也不知要做些什么鬼鬼祟祟的勾当。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    }
  ],
